<h3>CHALET DEALS</H3>


<p>There are a stack of amazing ski holidays on the market with massive reductions including Christmas &amp; New Year. We feature them all on our site but as each operator is offering something different you may find it easier to give one of our ski holiday experts a call 020 7801 1080.</p>

<p>Featured on the right are four chalet or chalet hotel properties that have a good deal on at the moment. These are just examples of the many, many fantastic chalet holidays that we feature in the Alps. To see all our <b>discounted</b> chalet holidays use the link below.</p>

<p class="btn"><a href="/ski-chalet-deals">See all our discounted chalet deals</a></p>



