<p></p>


<p></p>


<p></p>

<p></p>


<p></p>

<p>First established in 1992 (and under the same management ever since) Alpine Answers is a specialist ski holiday company and winter sports travel agency based in Battersea, London. Collectively we know the Alps and North America better than anyone on the planet. We've booked tens of thousands of ski holidays and will probably know your next trip's needs even before you do! We're constantly in touch with all the ski tour operators (we work with over 170 separate ski holiday companies) and pride ourselves on staying on top of the market.</p>

<p>We mostly sell <a href="http://www.alpineanswers.co.uk/ski-chalets" target="_blank" title="Search, sort and browse through all our chalet holidays"><b>catered chalet holidays</b></a> to the Alps (and some self catered chalets too) but we also sell <a href="http://www.alpineanswers.co.uk/ski-hotels" target="_blank" title="Browse through all our ski hotels"><b>hotel holidays</b></a> which can either be 'off the shelf' packaged holidays with respected tour operators or entirely bespoke tailormade hotel stays that we put together for you with scheduled flights and private taxi transfers. Whether you are two people or two hundred people we are here to help find and book your best ski holiday yet.</p>

